dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line data layer represents roads for Green County, Wisconsin in 2012. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Green_Roads_2012.gdb.[To be used by Green County Sheriff's Dispatcher's through their third party E911 dispatching and reporting system created by Spillman Technologies. Data created in conjunction with State E911 update grant.Features were derived from a variety of sources including deeds, descriptions, subdivision maps, certified survey maps, easements, and right of way maps. These source materials were of varying scale and date. This coverage provides a representation of the geometry and topology of tax parcels within the County, and is suitable as a reference layer within the County's GIS.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[This layer is intended as a base layer for use with other digital data developed by agencies within Green County.]
